            <p>Statue: <bibl type="hbi" n="rrrs1999"><author>R. R. R. Smith</author> (<date>1999</date>) <biblScope>161-2</biblScope></bibl>; <bibl type="hbi" n="rrrs2001"><author>R. R. R. Smith</author>, '<title level="a">A portait monument for Julian and Theodosius</title>' in C. Reusser ed. <title level="m">Griechenland in der Kaiserzeit</title> (Berlin, <date>2001</date>) <biblScope>125-136</biblScope></bibl>.</p>
         </div>
